#. [message]: speaker=unit
msgid ""
"This book claims that east of the jagged mountains in Gladerin Forest lives "
"a race of mysterious tree-folk. These 'elves' are said to be highly "
"secretive, yet fiercely protective of their woodland kingdom."
msgstr ""

